               <p>JOHN HAMILTON. I am <rs id="t18270712-111-viclabel608" type="occupation">cook on board a ship</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18270712-111-victim644 t18270712-111-viclabel608"></join>. The prisoner lodged with me; my clothes came from the mangle last Friday, and next morning I missed them from my chest; he said he had not got them; I found them in the officer's possession.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18270712-111-person645">
                  JOHN 
                  SHIELDS
               <interp inst="t18270712-111-person645" type="surname" value="SHIELDS"></interp>
